    ODHNotebook -->|"creates routes"| IngressCtrl[OpenShift Ingress Controller<br/>Route Processing]
    ODHNotebook -->|"provisions certs"| CertMgr[OpenShift Service CA<br/>Certificate Manager]
    ODHNotebook -->|"resolves images"| ImageStream[OpenShift ImageStream API<br/>Image Registry]

    %% Integration Points (Consuming ODH Services)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|"creates notebooks"| ODHNotebook

    %% Integration Points (Notebook Controller provides to other components)
    ODHNotebook -->|"enables access to"| NotebookPods[Notebook Pods<br/>Jupyter Workloads]

    %% Service Mesh (Alternative to OAuth)
    ODHNotebook -.->|"optional integration"| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh<br/>mTLS between services]

    %% Platform APIs
    ODHNotebook -->|"API operations"| K8sAPIServer[Kubernetes API Server<br/>HTTPS/443]

